# LLM Anti-Cheating Configuration

Per-project configuration file.
Copy this file to `.claude/llm-anti-cheating.local.md` to use.

---
mode: auto
level: balanced
---

## Configuration Options

### mode
- `auto` (default): Auto-inject policy at SessionStart + reminders on each prompt
- `manual`: Disable auto-injection, call via `/llm-ac` only

### level
- `balanced` (default): Minor violations allowed with proper labeling
- `strict`: All violations require immediate stop and user approval
